<h2>MVC and Its Benefits</h2>
<p>
    MVC is an architecture, it is a not a framework or any programming language. MVC stands for Model View Controller.
    MVC gives us a coding standard which is very helpful in making huge application and maintain readability and understanding
    of the code easy.
</p>
<h3>Benefits of MVC</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        Development of the application becomes fast.
    </li>
    <li>
        Easy for multiple developers to collaborate and work together.
    </li>
    <li>
        Easier to Update the application.
    </li>
    <li>
        Easier to Debug as we have multiple levels properly written in the application.
    </li>

</ul>

